  2017,"10",/general-conference/2017/10/the-eternal-everyday,Elder Quentin L. Cook,77,"As Nelson Mandela said, “Resentment is like drinking poison and then hoping it will kill your enemies” (in Jessica Durando, “15 of Nelson Mandela’s Best Quotes,”USA Today,Dec. 5, 2013, usatoday.com)."
  2017,"10",/general-conference/2017/10/the-eternal-everyday,Elder Quentin L. Cook,78,"Ether 12:26, 27; emphasis added."
