  2017,"10",/general-conference/2017/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,President Henry B. Eyring,9,Any opposed may so indicate.
  2017,"10",/general-conference/2017/10/the-sustaining-of-church-officers,President Henry B. Eyring,10,"It is proposed that we sustain the counselors in the First Presidency and the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles as prophets, seers, and revelators."
